does not amount to an integral portion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwrN","text_ar":"كُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba AlHus~aAbu Alkusuwra baEoDahaA","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ الحُسَّابُ الكُسُورَ بَعْضَهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY baEoDK","text_ar":"فِى بَعْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The calculator multiplied the fractions together"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Little in quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"number:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though it were a fraction of much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A crease, wrinkle, ply plait,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in skin, and in a garment or piece of cloth; (JK, S, * K, * voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gar~N","text_ar":"غَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gur~","text_ar":"غُرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so accord. to the explanation of the pl. in the present art. in the TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makosirN","text_ar":"مَكْسِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (accord. to the explanations of its pl. in the S, Mgh, Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDonN","text_ar":"غَضْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwrN","text_ar":"كُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK, S, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gar~N","text_ar":"غَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and TA in the present art.;) and of the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makaAsiru","text_ar":"مَكَاسِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Mgh, Msb, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDonN","text_ar":"غَضْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; &c.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwrN","text_ar":"كُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.       -A2-  [As a conventional term in grammar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vowel-sound, well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the sign for which is termed ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasorapN","text_ar":"كَسْرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","ISd"]},{"entry_id":"n36969","headword_ar":"كِسْرٌ","root":"ksr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasorN","text_ar":"كَسْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, &c.,) the latter of which is [said to be] of higher authority ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaY","text_ar":"اَعْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":") than the former, [but this is doubtful, for the former is certainly the more common,] (TA,)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2612},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of a limb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a complete limb:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a limb by itself, which is not mixed with another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half of a bone, with the flesh that is upon it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bone upon which there is not much flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and which is broken;"},{"kind":"text","text":"otherwise it is not thus called: (S) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any bone:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a limb"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel: (TA:) or of a human being or other: (ISd. TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akosaArN","text_ar":"اَكْسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwrN","text_ar":"كُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisru qabiyHK","text_ar":"كِسرُ قَبِيحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabiyHK","text_ar":"قَبِيحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasoru","text_ar":"كَسْرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bone of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAEid","text_ar":"سَاعِد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper half of the arm, from the part next the middle to the elbow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Umawee, S, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabiyHN","text_ar":"قَبِيحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ksr HasanK","text_ar":"كسر حَسَنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The upper part of that bone."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisorN","text_ar":"كِسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasorN","text_ar":"كَسْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two sides thereof that descends from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqataAni","text_ar":"طَرِيقَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning the two outer poles of the middle row]; every tent having two such, on the right and left: (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~ap","text_ar":"شُقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblong piece of cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xibaA='","text_ar":"خِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$q~h","text_ar":"شقّه"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is folded"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"creased"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"takas~ara watavan~aY","text_ar":"تَكَسَّرَ وَتَثَنَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$q~p","text_ar":"شقّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is next the ground, from where its"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the tent's)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two sides are folded"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino Hayovu yukosaru jaAnibaAhu","text_ar":"مِنْ حَيْثُ يُكْسَرُ جَانِبَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on thy right hand, and thy left."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S.) ―         -b4-  Also, (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasorN","text_ar":"كَسْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[only], (TA,) [but for this limitation there appears no reason,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A side"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) of anything; as, [for instance,] of a desert: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akosaArN","text_ar":"اَكْسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwrN","text_ar":"كُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. in all the senses: see above]. (K.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qidorN kisorN","text_ar":"قِدْرٌ كِسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akosaArN","text_ar":"اَكْسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inaA='N A^akosaArN","text_ar":"اـِنَا=ءٌ اَكْسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jafonapN A^akosaArN","text_ar":"جَفْنَةٌ اَكْسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) A cooking-pot, (TA,) and a vessel, (IAar,) and a bowl, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed of several pieces"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"joined together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K:) because of its greatness or its oldness: as though, in the second and following phrases, the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ksr","text_ar":"كسر"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to every distinct part of it. (TA.) ―         -b6-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kusuwrN","text_ar":"كُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below."}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S","AHeyth","A","IAar"]}]}}